    "faq": {
      "type": "section",
      "blocks": {
        "section_heading": {
          "type": "text",
          "name": "Section heading",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<h2>Questions before you subscribe</h2>",
            "type_preset": "h2",
            "width": "fit-content",
            "alignment": "center",
            "color": "var(--color-foreground-heading)"
          }
        },
        "accordion": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "name": "FAQ accordion",
          "settings": {
            "icon": "caret",
            "dividers": true,
            "type_preset": "h6",
            "inherit_color_scheme": true
          },
          "blocks": {
            "q0": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "Pre-order question",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Wait — this is a pre-order?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "stopwatch"
              },
              "blocks": {
                "q0_answer": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "name": "Answer",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Yes. We're launching with a pre-order window. First boxes ship the first week of August 2026. Your card is charged today and you lock in your tier — after the first box, the regular monthly cadence kicks in (boxes ship on the 15th of every month).</p><p>Founding pre-order subscribers get first dibs on limited drops and a small thank-you item in their first box.</p>",
                    "type_preset": "rte"
                  }
                }
              },
              "block_order": ["q0_answer"]
            },
            "q1": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "Shipping question",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "When does my box ship after the first one?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "box"
              },
              "blocks": {
                "q1_answer": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "name": "Answer",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>After the August 2026 launch box, the regular cadence kicks in: boxes ship on the 15th of every month. Order by the 10th to receive that month's drop — anything later ships the following month. Free US shipping on every tier.</p>",
                    "type_preset": "rte"
                  }
                }
              },
              "block_order": ["q1_answer"]
            },
            "q2": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "Cancel question",
              "settings": {
                "heading": "Can I cancel anytime?",
                "open_by_default": false,
                "icon": "check_box"
              },
              "blocks": {
                "q2_answer": {
                  "type": "text",
                  "name": "Answer",
                  "settings": {
                    "text": "<p>Yes. No commitment, no cancellation fee. Manage your subscription from your account at any time. Skip a month, swap tiers, or pause when life gets in the way.</p>",
                    "type_preset": "rte"
                  }
                }
              },
              "block_order": ["q2_answer"]
            },
            "q3": {
              "type": "_accordion-row",
              "name": "Quality question",
              "settings": {
